headline: 2 AI Stocks to Buy in June
summary: CoreWeave is a pure-play investment in the growing demand for AI data centers.  Advanced Micro Devices continues to see strong demand for its data center chips.  Artificial intelligence (AI) is sweeping across the corporate landscape, increasing labor productivity and the speed of innovation.
